title: Marshawn Lynch to miss second straight game (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,166 Marshawn Lynch to miss second straight game (Yahoo Sports) Marshawn Lynch will miss a second straight week for the Seattle Seahawks due to a hamstring strain. The team on Friday officially ruled Lynch out for Sunday's game against the Cincinnati Bengals. Lynch injured his hamstring in the second quarter of the team's 26-0 victory over the Chicago Bears in Week 3.
